name: 娜塔莉·利康蒂
name_full: 娜塔莉·利康蒂 Natalie Liconti
introduction: Natalie Liconti is a Canadian, non-binary performer. They are best known for their role as Sterling on Netflix/CW's In The Dark (2020) and Jeff Barnaby's Blood Quantum (Canadian Screen Awards, Prix Iris, Catalonian International Film Festival, Toronto International Film Festival). They grew up in Toronto, Canada and studied at McGill University and the University of Glasgow.- IMDb Mini Biography By: Anonymous
